        "id": "prompt_template",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Explain the following topic so that the given audience genuinely understands it.\n\nTopic: {{ topic }}\nAudience: {{ audience }}\n\nWrite your explanation in exactly four parts, in this order:\n1. **In one sentence** — the core idea, no jargon.\n2. **Analogy** — compare it to something the audience already knows.\n3. **Example** — a concrete, everyday instance of it in action.\n4. **Common misconception** — one thing people often get wrong about it, corrected.\n\nMatch your vocabulary and tone to the audience. Keep the whole answer under 200 words."
        },
